oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Postcard from New York Department of State Corporations
oai_dc:dc.dc:subject: Commonwealth Finance Corporation; Soehner family; 1960s;
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Addressed to: Mrs. E.O. Soehner -- 3104 N. Nagle Ave. -- Chicago, Ill. Body: State of New York - Dept. of State Corporations Bureau - Albany, N. Y. -- Commonwealth Finance Corporation is a South Dokota Corporation authorized to do business in this state 10/5/16 NY County and Certificate of Surrender of Authority was filed 4/19/21. John P. Lomenzo, Secretary of State
